lead_paragraph: Australia coach Michael Cheika has recalled lock Kane Douglas and number eight Lopeti Timani among four changes adding size to the side for Saturday's final test of the autumn series against England at Twickenham.

headline.print_headline: Douglas Recalled as Australia Make Four Changes
headline.main: Douglas Recalled as Australia Make Four Changes
